Technology.技术。


Arweave is a network that connects those with disk space to spare with those who need permanent data storage. This system offers unparalleled levels of data replication and security for users, as well as financial incentives for those storing data, without a middleman. Arweave 是一个网络，它将那些有磁盘空间的人与那些需要永久数据存储的人联系起来。该系统为用户提供了无与伦比的数据复制和安全级别，并为那些存储数据的人提供了经济激励，没有中间人。

Rather than operating as a traditional company or foundation, the Arweave network is fully decentralised, meaning that anyone can store data in the network or offer storage space, without there being a leader or centralised point of failure. Through decentralization, Arweave offers a new standard of data archiving and storage: one in which information is globally replicated on hundreds of machines, impervious to fire, flood, or intentional damage. Arweave 网络不是作为传统公司或基金会运营，而是完全去中心化的，这意味着任何人都可以在网络中存储数据或提供存储空间，而不会出现领导者或集中故障点。通过去中心化，Arweave 提供了一种新的数据归档和存储标准：信息在全球范围内复制到数百台机器上，不受火灾、洪水或故意损坏的影响。

Papers文件

Learn how the Arweave network works in detail in the project’s yellow paper.在项目的黄皮书中详细了解 Arweave 网络的工作原理。

For historical context, you can also read the June 2018 Arweave light paper, and the original August 2017 whitepaper. The founding team’s Arweave blog also contains documents and articles about the evolution of the protocol during its early stages, plus current updates on the project’s progress.对于历史背景，您还可以阅读 2018 年 6 月的 Arweave 轻型白皮书和 2017 年 8 月的原始白皮书。创始团队的 Arweave 博客还包含有关协议在早期阶段演变的文档和文章，以及项目进展的当前更新。

Below you will find a simple overview of the core technologies in the Arweave protocol.您将在下面找到 Arweave 协议中核心技术的简单概述。

Blockweaves and Proof of AccessBlockweaves 和访问证明

The core technology that powers the Arweave is the blockweave. Just as a blockchain is a linked collection of blocks containing transactions, a blockweave -- specifically designed for the Arweave protocol -- is a set of blocks that contain data, linking to multiple previous blocks from the network. This data structure allows the network to an enforce that miners provide a ‘Proof of Access’ (PoA) to old data in order to add new blocks.为 Arweave 提供动力的核心技术是 blockweave。正如区块链是包含交易的块的链接集合一样，blockweave——专门为 Arweave 协议设计——是一组包含数据的块，链接到网络中的多个先前块。这种数据结构允许网络强制矿工向旧数据提供“访问证明”（PoA）以添加新块。

Unlike in a traditional blockchain, where miners are forced to expend electricity in order to earn tokens, in the Arweave network miners are also encouraged to replicate valuable data (the information stored in the network) in order to gain tokens. This mechanism offsets the value that is normally wasted in blockchain networks, with useful, energy efficient storage of data.与传统区块链中矿工被迫消耗电力以获得代币不同，在 Arweave 网络中，还鼓励矿工复制有价值的数据（存储在网络中的信息）以获得代币。这种机制通过有用的、节能的数据存储抵消了通常在区块链网络中浪费的价值。

You can read more about Arweave’s blockweave and proof of access mechanisms in chapter 2.1 of the Arweave yellow paper.您可以在 Arweave 黄皮书的第 2.1 章中阅读有关 Arweave 的块编织和访问证明机制的更多信息。

Storage Endowment存储禀赋

Arweave’s data storage is backed by sustainable, transparent economics that allow users to perpetuate the replication of information forever. Arweave 的数据存储以可持续、透明的经济为后盾，使用户能够永远复制信息。

The Arweave’s economic mechanism is similar to a traditional economic endowment structure. When a piece of data is added to the Arweave network, the user pays a ‘principle’ upfront, on which ‘interest’ in the form of storage purchasing power is accrued. Over time, interest on this one-time upfront payment is given to those that offer hard drive space so that they can profit from their storage contributions. By using extremely conservative estimates for storage pricing, Arweave ensures the long-term viability of the network’s endowment. Arweave 的经济机制类似于传统的经济禀赋结构。当一条数据被添加到 Arweave 网络时，用户会预先支付一笔“本金”，以存储购买力的形式产生“利息”。随着时间的推移，这种一次性预付款的利息将提供给那些提供硬盘驱动器空间的人，以便他们可以从他们的存储贡献中获利。通过对存储定价使用极其保守的估计，Arweave 确保了网络捐赠的长期可行性。

For more details regarding the network’s economics, expectations and mathematics, please see chapter 3.2.2 of the yellow paper. 有关网络经济学、期望和数学的更多详细信息，请参阅黄皮书第 3.2.2 章。

The Permaweb永久网

On top of the core Arweave data storage layer, sits the permaweb. The permaweb is a collection of interlinked documents and applications -- just like the traditional web -- except all contents are entirely permanent. Because the Arweave network itself is built on top of HTTP (the protocol from which the traditional web arises), browsers have access to all of the data stored in the network. As the Arweave network itself is agnostic to its contents, the permaweb can be used to store all kinds of information -- from wikis, to PDFs, to videos, and web applications. Once included in the network, these files are always accessible, from any place in the world, at any time. Further, once submitted nobody (including their original uploader) can alter them in anyway -- enforcing consumer integrity for applications, and verifiability for documents, forever. To find out how it feels to use the permaweb by browsing some applications built by the community here. 在核心 Arweave 数据存储层之上，是 permaweb。 permaweb 是相互关联的文档和应用程序的集合——就像传统的网络一样——除了所有内容都是完全永久的。因为 Arweave 网络本身是建立在 HTTP（传统网络的起源协议）之上的，浏览器可以访问存储在网络中的所有数据。由于 Arweave 网络本身对其内容不可知，因此 permaweb 可用于存储各种信息——从维基到 PDF、视频和 Web 应用程序。一旦包含在网络中，这些文件就可以随时从世界任何地方访问。此外，一旦提交，任何人（包括他们的原始上传者）都不能以任何方式更改它们——永远强制执行应用程序的消费者完整性和文档的可验证性。通过浏览此处社区构建的一些应用程序，了解使用 permaweb 的感受。

Content Moderation内容审核

Just like the traditional web, potential abuse of the permaweb is a serious issue. The community of developers and storers that maintain the network treat these issues carefully. Unlike the traditional web, the permaweb has tools for democratic moderation of its content built into the core of the protocol – putting control of the new web back into the hands of the people, users. 就像传统网络一样，永久网络的潜在滥用是一个严重的问题。维护网络的开发者和存储者社区会谨慎对待这些问题。与传统网络不同，permaweb 在协议的核心中内置了对其内容进行民主审核的工具——将新网络的控制权交还给人们和用户。


How it works怎么运行的

When someone submits a transaction to the Arweave network, data storers are given the choice of whether to replicate the associated data. The maintainers of the network are able to filter and screen the transaction in whichever manner they choose, checking against known illicit material, scanning the data with computer vision software, et cetera. You can learn more about how content is moderated in the Arweave protocol in the yellowpaper. The founding Arweave team is working with the Internet Watch Foundation to provide the maintainers of the Arweave network with the capabilities that they need to keep their systems and the permaweb safe from abusive material. Data storers can also elect not to replicate any material from the network, for any reason, if they feel that it is inappropriate for storage. Finally, those that maintain gateways (the servers you will likely use to view the permaweb) can also apply content moderation policies to further safeguard their users. If you would like a piece of content found on an arweave.net gateway to be removed, please contact us and you will receive a response shortly.当有人向 Arweave 网络提交交易时，数据存储者可以选择是否复制相关数据。网络的维护者能够以他们选择的任何方式过滤和筛选交易，检查已知的非法材料，使用计算机视觉软件扫描数据等等。您可以在黄皮书的 Arweave 协议中详细了解如何管理内容。 Arweave 的创始团队正在与 Internet Watch Foundation 合作，为 Arweave 网络的维护者提供他们所需的功能，以确保他们的系统和 permaweb 免受滥用材料的侵害。如果数据存储者认为不适合存储，他们也可以出于任何原因选择不从网络复制任何材料。最后，那些维护网关（您可能用来查看 permaweb 的服务器）也可以应用内容审核策略来进一步保护他们的用户。如果您希望删除在 arweave.net 网关上找到的内容，请联系我们，您将很快收到回复。
